    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there\u2019s not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
