      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that remains within factory tolerances. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip M-Variable differential. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement already completed. Performance is sharpened by a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein B6 dampers and OEM bushings, maintaining the original handling dynamics. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment, while the interior displays zero bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically synchronized, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
